info.name: Little Shark's Outings
info.description: The adventures of a baby shark in nostalgia-filled Yauo Town.  Whether it's cider on a summer day, freeze pops, radio calisthenics, festival stalls, or hanging out with friends, the world sparkles when reflected in the eyes of the baby shark.

moreInfo.synonyms: Little Shark's Outings, Outgoing Baby Shark
